name: Gerard Dacudao
text: Ok, guys need to go.  Just think about this, we have 20million Filipinos in extreme poverty.  10million ofws.  Time for a change in the system.  Lets just stick to the platform of a du30 presidency.  He is pro business, pro decentralizatio n via federalism, he is anti corruption via a parliamentary form of govt.  A proven way to improve govt accountbility.
